You need to use [**`$group`**][1] aggregation with [**`$sum`**][2] and [**`$push`**][3] accumulator

    db.collection.aggregate([
      { &quot;$group&quot;: {
        &quot;_id&quot;: &quot;$group&quot;,
        &quot;items&quot;: { &quot;$push&quot;: &quot;$$ROOT&quot; },
        &quot;total_qty&quot;: { &quot;$sum&quot;: &quot;$qty&quot; }
      }},
      { &quot;$sort&quot;: { &quot;total_qty&quot;: -1 }}
    ])


  [1]: https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/operator/aggregation/group/
  [2]: https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/operator/aggregation/sum/
  [3]: https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/operator/aggregation/push/

